everyone wants in a surgeon.

14
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,770
They maybe know
what they're doing.

15
00:00:31,814 --> 00:00:33,381
Always have a plan...
I told you that.

16
00:00:33,424 --> 00:00:34,860
Suction, Meredith!

17
00:00:34,904 --> 00:00:36,340
It's the moment
when fear sets in.

18
00:00:36,384 --> 00:00:38,473
