finished.

114
00:04:13,557 --> 00:04:15,342
He woke up Luna.

115
00:04:15,385 --> 00:04:17,387
O-Oh, oh!

116
00:04:17,431 --> 00:04:18,954
Wow.

117
00:04:20,521 --> 00:04:21,826
Is it show tunes?

118
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,611
