No. It's more like
one long note.

120
00:04:27,528 --> 00:04:28,790
So like...

121
00:04:28,833 --> 00:04:32,097
♪ Do, re, mi, fa, Jo

122
00:04:32,141 --> 00:04:34,926
Are you gonna
break up with him at lunch

123
