out in Bellingham this Saturday.

133
00:05:04,782 --> 00:05:08,308
Unless my son shows up,
but he's taking his sweet time.

134
00:05:08,351 --> 00:05:09,396
Mm-hmm.

135
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:11,572
Well, listen up.

136
00:05:11,615 --> 00:05:13,008
