I want to see butts in seats,

210
00:08:24,634 --> 00:08:25,809
needles in arms.

211
00:08:25,853 --> 00:08:27,550
Tell your friends.

212
00:08:27,594 --> 00:08:30,553
Okay. People's blood
isn't gonna donate itself.

213
00:08:30,597 --> 00:08:31,641
